ActNational Housing Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Infrastructure and Communities as the Minister for the Purposes of the National Housing Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-949 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of INFRASTRUCTURE AND COMMUNITIES, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the NATIONAL HOUSING ACT.
